  description="Fulfillment services for online stores: storage, packing, shipping from 18 UAH/order. 6,000 shipments/day, 2 warehouses near Kyiv."
  canonical="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/en/fulfillment-for-online-stores/"
  lang="en"
  ogImage="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/images/mtp-fulfillment-warehouse-hero.webp"
  schema={schemaJson}
>
<Fragment slot="head">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/en/fulfillment-for-online-stores/">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="uk" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/ua/fulfilment-dlya-internet-magazynu/">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="ru" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/fulfilment-dlya-internet-magazynu/">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/ua/fulfilment-dlya-internet-magazynu/">
</Fragment>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
<div class="hero-bg"></div>
<div class="hero-content">
<div class="badge">FULFILLMENT</div>
<h1>Fulfillment for<br>Online Stores</h1>
<p class="hero-sub">You sell &mdash; we ship. Goods receiving, storage, packing and delivery across Ukraine. From 18&nbsp;UAH per shipment.</p>
<form class="hero-form" id="heroForm"><input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="+380XXXXXXXXX" maxlength="25" required autocomplete="tel" aria-label="Phone"><button type="submit">Get a quote &#8594;</button></form>
<div class="hero-note">Free consultation &#183; Custom quote in 15 min</div>
</div>
<div class="hero-stats">
<div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-val">6,000</div><div class="hero-stat-label">shipments/day</div></div>
<div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-val">150+</div><div class="hero-stat-label">active clients</div></div>
<div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-val">30 sec</div><div class="hero-stat-label">order picking</div>
</section></div>
</section>
<div class="hero-guarantees">
  <span>&#10003; No long-term contract</span>
  <span>&#10003; Trial period</span>
  <span>&#10003; Exit in 1 day</span>
</div>

<!-- BENEFITS -->
<section class="benefits"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">BENEFITS</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">Why online stores choose MTP</h2>
<div class="ben-grid">
<div class="ben-card"><div class="ben-num">30"</div><h3>30-second picking</h3><p>Conveyor packing stations and WMS automation &mdash; every order picked and labeled in half a minute</p></div>
<div class="ben-card"><div class="ben-num">17</div><h3>17 days free on Nova Poshta</h3><p>Parcels stored at Nova Poshta for 17 days at no extra cost. Free returns via Nova Poshta</p></div>
<div class="ben-card"><div class="ben-num">8 hrs</div><h3>8 hours per month</h3><p>That is how much time the average client spends on logistics after switching to fulfillment. The rest goes to marketing and sales</p></div>
<div class="ben-card"><div class="ben-num">API</div><h3>Integration in 2 hours</h3><p>KeyCRM, SalesDrive, Horoshop, WooCommerce, OpenCart, Shopify, Prom.ua, Rozetka &mdash; connected on the same day</p></div>
<div class="ben-card"><div class="ben-num">3x</div><h3>3 generators + Starlink</h3><p>Uninterrupted operations even during blackouts. 2 fibre-optic providers &mdash; zero days of downtime since 2022</p></div>
<div class="ben-card"><div class="ben-num">99.5%</div><h3>Order accuracy</h3><p>Barcode scanning at every stage, photo documentation &mdash; minimal errors, minimal claims</p></div>
</section></div></section>

<section class="warehouse-tour">
<div class="tour-inner">
<div class="tour-text">
<div class="badge">WAREHOUSE</div>
<h2>Your orders —<br>our business</h2>
<p>Watch how we pick, pack, and ship thousands of online store orders every day from our fulfillment center.</p>
<button class="tour-btn" onclick="openVideoModal('bHY3cFF9SlI')">&#9654; See the process</button>
</div>
<div class="tour-video">
<div class="video-thumb" onclick="openVideoModal('bHY3cFF9SlI')" style="cursor:pointer">
<img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/bHY3cFF9SlI/maxresdefault.jpg" onerror="this.src='https://img.youtube.com/vi/bHY3cFF9SlI/hqdefault.jpg'" alt="How MTP Group fulfills online store orders — warehouse video" width="640" height="360" loading="lazy">
<div class="play-overlay"><div class="play-btn-large">&#9654;</div><span>Fulfillment in action</span></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section></div>
</section>

<!-- CASE STUDY -->
<section class="case"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge">CLIENT CASE</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">Cosmetics store: from 80 to 400 orders per day</h2>
<div class="case-inner">
<div class="case-text">
<p>A natural cosmetics store contacted MTP Group when order volume exceeded 80 per day. Two packers could not keep up, parcels were shipped late, and Nova Poshta started charging penalties for delayed pickups.</p>
<blockquote>&laquo;We spent 6 hours a day packing instead of launching new products and working with influencers&raquo;</blockquote>
<p><strong>MTP solution:</strong> full onboarding in 2 days. KeyCRM integration, transfer of 3,000 SKUs to the warehouse, branded packaging setup with tissue paper and stickers. Within a month the client tripled their ad budget because logistics was no longer the bottleneck.</p>
</div>
<div class="case-stats">
<div class="case-stat"><div class="case-stat-val">80 &rarr; 400</div><div class="case-stat-label">orders/day</div></div>
<div class="case-stat"><div class="case-stat-val">&minus;70%</div><div class="case-stat-label">logistics costs</div></div>
<div class="case-stat"><div class="case-stat-val">2 days</div><div class="case-stat-label">full onboarding</div></div>
</div>
</section></div></section>

<!-- TARIFFS -->
<section class="pricing"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">RATES 2026</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">How much does fulfillment cost</h2>
<div class="price-table">
<div class="price-row price-header"><span>Service</span><span>Condition</span><span>Price</span></div>
<div class="price-row"><span>Order shipping</span><span>200+ orders/day</span><span>from 18 UAH</span></div>
<div class="price-row"><span>Order shipping</span><span>100-199 orders/day</span><span>from 20 UAH</span></div>
<div class="price-row"><span>Order shipping</span><span>50-99 orders/day</span><span>from 22 UAH</span></div>
<div class="price-row"><span>Order shipping</span><span>0-49 orders/day</span><span>from 26 UAH</span></div>
<div class="price-row"><span>Storage</span><span>per m&sup3;/month</span><span>from 650 UAH</span></div>
<div class="price-row"><span>Goods receiving</span><span>per unit</span><span>from 3 UAH</span></div>
<div class="price-row price-highlight"><span>Minimum fee</span><span>per month</span><span>5,000 UAH</span></div>
</div>
<p class="price-note">Price decreases with volume growth. Exact quote &mdash; free within 15 minutes.</p>
<div class="price-cta"><button onclick="document.getElementById('finalForm').querySelector('input').focus();window.scrollTo({top:document.getElementById('ctaSection').offsetTop,behavior:'smooth'})">Calculate for my store &#8594;</button></div>
</div></section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="faq"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge">FAQ</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">Frequently asked questions</h2>
<div class="faq-list">
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Can a foreign-based online store use MTP fulfillment to sell in Ukraine?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. International e-commerce brands ship inventory to our Kyiv-area warehouse via DHL, FedEx, or freight forwarder. We integrate with your Shopify or WooCommerce store, process orders, and ship to Ukrainian buyers via Nova Poshta. No local entity required for the test phase.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">What CRM and e-commerce platforms integrate with your WMS?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>We connect with KeyCRM, SalesDrive, Horoshop, WooCommerce, OpenCart, Shopify, Magento, Prom.ua, and Rozetka. Any platform with a REST API can be integrated in 2-4 hours. Real-time inventory sync and automated order pulling are included.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Do you offer branded packaging for DTC stores?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. We support custom boxes, tissue paper, branded tape, thank-you cards, promotional flyers, and sample inserts. You provide the materials or we source them locally. Branded packing adds 2.50 UAH (~$0.06) per item.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">How do you handle seasonal order spikes like Black Friday?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Our conveyor-based packing stations scale to 6,000 shipments per day. We pre-allocate capacity for clients who share forecasts 2 weeks in advance. No surcharges for peak volume &mdash; your per-order rate stays the same.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">What is the order cutoff time for same-day shipping?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Orders received via API before 14:00 Kyiv time (UTC+2) ship the same day. Nova Poshta picks up from our warehouse 4 times daily. Late-afternoon orders ship on the next business day.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">How does cash-on-delivery (COD) work for Ukrainian orders?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>COD is the dominant payment method in Ukraine, accounting for roughly 60% of online orders. Nova Poshta collects payment from the buyer on delivery and transfers the funds to your account. We monitor COD statuses in real-time via Telegram alerts.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Can I manage inventory across my own website and marketplaces simultaneously?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. Our WMS maintains a single inventory pool synced in real-time across all connected channels &mdash; your Shopify store, Rozetka, Prom.ua, and others. Zero risk of overselling. Stock levels update automatically after every order and return.</p></div></div>
</div>
</div></section>

<!-- SEO ARTICLE -->
<section class="article-section">
<div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">USEFUL INFO</div>
<h2>Outsourcing e-commerce fulfillment in Ukraine: a guide for international DTC brands</h2>
<div class="article-content">
<h3>Why international DTC brands are choosing Ukrainian fulfillment</h3>
<p>Ukraine's e-commerce market has grown by over 25% year-over-year, reaching an estimated $8 billion in gross merchandise value. For international direct-to-consumer brands, the opportunity is clear: 37 million active internet users, low competition from foreign sellers, and fulfillment costs that run 50-70% lower than comparable services in Poland, Germany, or the UK. A single warehouse near Kyiv provides next-day delivery coverage across the entire country.</p>

<h3>The CRM integration advantage</h3>
<p>One of the biggest concerns for international online stores is whether their existing tech stack will work with a Ukrainian 3PL. The answer is yes. Modern fulfillment operators like MTP Group integrate directly with Shopify, WooCommerce, OpenCart, Magento, and any platform that offers a REST API. Orders flow automatically from your storefront to the warehouse. Inventory levels sync in real-time. Shipping labels are generated without manual input. The entire integration process takes 2-4 hours, and your existing checkout experience remains unchanged.</p>

<h3>Branded packaging: building customer loyalty from the unboxing</h3>
<p>For DTC brands, the unboxing moment is part of the product experience. MTP Group offers custom branded packaging options including printed boxes, tissue paper, branded tape, thank-you cards, promotional flyers, and sample inserts. You can ship your own packaging materials to the warehouse or work with our local sourcing contacts to produce them in Ukraine at a fraction of EU manufacturing costs. The cost of adding custom inserts is 2.50 UAH (~$0.06) per item.</p>

<h3>How COD payments work in Ukraine</h3>
<p>Cash-on-delivery remains a major payment method in Ukrainian e-commerce, accounting for approximately 60% of all online purchases. This is unfamiliar territory for most international sellers accustomed to prepaid models. When you ship via Nova Poshta, the carrier collects payment from the buyer and transfers the funds to your designated account. MTP Group provides real-time COD monitoring via Telegram, so you always know which payments have been collected and which are pending.</p>

<h3>Scaling through seasonal peaks</h3>
<p>Ukrainian e-commerce follows a distinct seasonal pattern: a steady build through September-October, a massive spike during Black Friday and New Year, and a strong spring rebound. MTP Group's conveyor-based packing stations handle up to 6,000 shipments per day without compromising quality. There are no peak-season surcharges. If you share your forecast 2 weeks before a planned promotion, we pre-allocate warehouse staff and packing station capacity to ensure every order ships the same day.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->


</Base>

<style is:global>
.hero{position:relative;min-height:90vh;background:var(--black);color:var(--white);display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:140px 0 0;overflow:hidden}
.hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(105deg,rgba(0,0,0,.88) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,.65) 55%,rgba(0,0,0,.45) 100%),url('https://img.youtube.com/vi/bHY3cFF9SlI/maxresdefault.jpg') center/cover no-repeat}
.hero-content{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:0 8vw;width:100%}
.hero-content::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:calc(8vw - 40px);top:0;height:100%;width:3px;background:var(--red)}
.hero h1{font-family:var(--fd);font-size:clamp(42px,5.5vw,80px);font-weight:400;line-height:.95;margin-bottom:28px}
.hero-sub{font-size:clamp(16px,1.8vw,19px);color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);line-height:1.7;max-width:580px;margin-bottom:40px}
.hero-form{display:flex;gap:12px;max-width:460px}
.hero-form input{flex:1;padding:16px 20px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-radius:4px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);color:#fff;font-size:15px;font-family:var(--fb);outline:none}
.hero-form input::placeholder{color:rgba(255,255,255,.25)}.hero-form input:focus{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)}
.hero-form button{padding:16px 24px;background:#e63329;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:4px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--fb);white-space:nowrap;transition:all .3s}
.hero-form button:hover{background:#c42b22}
.hero-note{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);margin-top:12px}
.hero-stats{display:flex;gap:32px;padding:48px 8vw 0;margin-top:auto;position:relative;z-index:2}
.hero-stat{border-top:3px solid var(--red);padding:20px 0;flex:1}
.hero-stat-val{font-family:var(--fd);font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,64px);font-weight:400;color:#fff;white-space:nowrap}
.hero-stat-label{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:4px}
.benefits{padding:100px 0}
.ben-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:#e0e0e0;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.ben-card{background:#fff;padding:36px 28px;transition:background .3s}.ben-card:hover{background:var(--gray)}
.ben-num{font-family:var(--fd);font-size:42px;color:var(--red);line-height:1;margin-bottom:12px}
.ben-card h3{font-size:17px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:6px}.ben-card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}
.case{padding:100px 0;background:#0a0a0a;color:#fff}
.case-inner{display:flex;gap:80px;align-items:center}
.case-text{flex:1.2}.case-text blockquote{font-family:var(--fd);font-style:italic;font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);line-height:1.5;border-left:3px solid var(--red);padding-left:20px;margin:20px 0}
.case-text p{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px}
.case-stats{flex:.8;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px}
.case-stat{text-align:center;padding:28px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:8px}
.case-stat-val{font-size:36px;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:4px}.case-stat-label{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px}
.pricing{padding:100px 0;background:var(--gray)}
